HeidelbergCement Eyes Better Rating, CEO Tells Boersen-Zeitung

-- B y   A n d r e a s   C r e m e r
-- 
2011-07-30T09:04:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-30/heidelbergcement-eyes-better-rating-ceo-tells-boersen-zeitung.html
HeidelbergCement AG (HEI)  is pursuing a
better  credit rating ,  Boersen-Zeitung  reported, citing Chief
Executive Officer  Bernd Scheifele .  “Next year we want to achieve the financial results that
are necessary for an investment-grade rating,” the newspaper
quoted the CEO as saying in an interview published online today.
“We have steadily improved.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andreas Cremer in Berlin at 
